---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us - MaizeSupply Pro" description="Learn about MaizeSupply Pro's mission, background, and commitment to supporting local farmers while providing premium maize supply services.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1>About MaizeSupply Pro</h1>
        <p>Connecting farmers with businesses through sustainable and reliable maize supply solutions</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Story -->
  <section class="section our-story">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid grid-2">
        <div class="story-content">
          <h2>Our Story</h2>
          <p>Founded in 2018, MaizeSupply Pro emerged from a vision to create a sustainable bridge between local maize farmers and the businesses that depend on quality grain supply. What started as a small operation supporting regional farmers has grown into a trusted network spanning multiple states.</p>
          <p>Our founders, with over 20 years of combined experience in agriculture and supply chain management, recognized the challenges both farmers and businesses faced in the maize supply chain. Farmers struggled to find reliable buyers for their harvest, while businesses dealt with inconsistent quality and unreliable supply.</p>
          <p>Today, we're proud to work with over 500 partner farmers and serve hundreds of businesses nationwide, maintaining our commitment to quality, sustainability, and fair trade practices that benefit everyone in our network.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="story-image">
          <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/1595108/pexels-photo-1595108.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1" alt="Maize farming and harvesting" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Mission & Vision -->
  <section class="section mission-vision">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid grid-2">
        <div class="mission-card">
          <div class="card-icon">🎯</div>
          <h3>Our Mission</h3>
          <p>To provide reliable, high-quality maize supply solutions while supporting sustainable farming practices and empowering local agricultural communities through fair trade partnerships.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="vision-card">
          <div class="card-icon">🌟</div>
          <h3>Our Vision</h3>
          <p>To become the leading maize supply partner that transforms agricultural communities and food security through innovative, sustainable, and equitable supply chain solutions.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Values -->
  <section class="section our-values">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Our Core Values</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-3">
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">🌱</div>
          <h3>Sustainability</h3>
          <p>We promote environmentally responsible farming practices and sustainable supply chain operations that protect our planet for future generations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">🤝</div>
          <h3>Partnership</h3>
          <p>We believe in building long-term relationships based on trust, mutual respect, and shared prosperity with farmers and business clients alike.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">✨</div>
          <h3>Quality</h3>
          <p>We maintain the highest standards in everything we do, from grain selection to final delivery, ensuring consistent excellence.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">⚡</div>
          <h3>Reliability</h3>
          <p>Our clients depend on us for consistent supply, and we take that responsibility seriously with dependable service and communication.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">💡</div>
          <h3>Innovation</h3>
          <p>We continuously improve our processes and adopt new technologies to enhance efficiency and service quality.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">❤️</div>
          <h3>Community</h3>
          <p>We're committed to strengthening agricultural communities and contributing to local economic development.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Commitment -->
  <section class="section our-commitment">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Our Commitment</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-2">
        <div class="commitment-content">
          <div class="commitment-item">
            <h3>🌾 To Local Farmers</h3>
            <p>We provide fair pricing, reliable purchase agreements, and support for sustainable farming practices. Our farmer development programs help improve yields and farming techniques.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="commitment-item">
            <h3>🏭 To Our Clients</h3>
            <p>We guarantee consistent quality, reliable delivery schedules, and competitive pricing. Our quality assurance processes ensure you receive only the finest maize.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="commitment-item">
            <h3>🌍 To the Environment</h3>
            <p>We promote sustainable farming practices, reduce waste in our supply chain, and work towards carbon-neutral operations through responsible transportation and packaging.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="commitment-item">
            <h3>🏘️ To Communities</h3>
            <p>We invest in local communities through education programs, infrastructure support, and economic development initiatives that strengthen rural areas.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="commitment-image">
          <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/5647021/pexels-photo-5647021.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1" alt="Community farming cooperation" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Team -->
  <section class="section our-team">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Leadership Team</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Meet the experienced professionals leading MaizeSupply Pro</p>
      <div class="grid grid-3">
        <div class="team-member">
          <div class="member-avatar">👨‍💼</div>
          <h3>Benard Atika</h3>
          <p class="member-role">Chief Executive Officer</p>
          <p>20+ years in agricultural supply chain management and sustainable farming initiatives.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="team-member">
          <div class="member-avatar">👩‍💼</div>
          <h3>Sheila Mwanga</h3>
          <p class="member-role">Head of Operations</p>
          <p>Expert in logistics and quality control with 15 years of experience in food supply networks.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="team-member">
          <div class="member-avatar">👨‍🌾</div>
          <h3>Leon Maina</h3>
          <p class="member-role">Director of Farmer Relations</p>
          <p>Agricultural specialist focused on farmer partnerships and sustainable farming practices.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call to Action -->
  <section class="section cta">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Partner with Us</h2>
        <p>Join our network of satisfied clients and partner farmers. Experience the difference of working with a trusted maize supply partner.</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started</a>
          <a href="/services" class="btn btn-outline">Learn More</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #22c55e 0%, #16a34a 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 120px 0 80px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-content h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .hero-content p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .our-story {
    background: white;
  }

  .story-content h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: #1f2937;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }

  .story-content p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #6b7280;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .story-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 450px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .mission-vision {
    background: #f9fafb;
  }

  .mission-card,
  .vision-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 40px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .mission-card:hover,
  .vision-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
  }

  .card-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .mission-card h3,
  .vision-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: #1f2937;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .mission-card p,
  .vision-card p {
    color: #6b7280;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .our-values {
    background: white;
  }

  .value-card {
    background: #f9fafb;
    padding: 30px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    border: 2px solid transparent;
  }

  .value-card:hover {
    border-color: #22c55e;
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    background: white;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.1);
  }

  .value-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .value-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #1f2937;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .value-card p {
    color: #6b7280;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .our-commitment {
    background: #f9fafb;
  }

  .commitment-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 30px;
  }

  .commitment-item h3 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: #1f2937;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .commitment-item p {
    color: #6b7280;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .commitment-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 450px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .our-team {
    background: white;
  }

  .team-member {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 30px 20px;
    background: #f9fafb;
    border-radius: 16px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .team-member:hover {
    background: white;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }

  .member-avatar {
    font-size: 4rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .team-member h3 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: #1f2937;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }

  .member-role {
    color: #22c55e;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .team-member p {
    color: #6b7280;
    line-height: 1.5;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .cta {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #22c55e 0%, #16a34a 100%);
    color: white;
  }

  .cta-content {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .cta-content p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  /* Responsive Design */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-content h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .hero-content p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .story-content h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .story-image img,
    .commitment-image img {
      height: 300px;
    }

    .cta-content h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .hero-content h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .story-content h2 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    .cta-content h2 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    .cta-content p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
  }
</style>